downloadTitle: Space Planning with Asset Data sample diagram for Visio 2010
downloadDescription: Help simplify asset management and space planning by incorporating asset information into a space plan using this Visio 2010 sample diagram.
detailsSection: Use this Microsoft Visio 2010 sample diagram to simplify asset management and space planning. This sample shows how you can create a space plan for your office and incorporate detailed asset information for the contents of each room, such as manufacturer, network name, IP address, hard drive size, installation and lease dates, and so on. This sample diagram could also be extended by adding more detail, such as human resources (HR) data about the occupants of each office from your HR database.
installInstructionSection:
Click Download to save the sample diagram to your computer.

To customize the data linked to the template, download Space Data.xlsx and populate it with your own space plan data.
